WEBVTT

00:00:35.970 --> 00:00:38.640
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.220
=Episode 20=

00:00:45.833 --> 00:00:47.416
I'm the Prince of Liao.

00:00:48.208 --> 00:00:49.500
How dare you treat me like this?

00:00:50.083 --> 00:00:52.333
Three days ago, perhaps.

00:00:52.833 --> 00:00:53.666
But now,

00:00:54.250 --> 00:00:55.333
you are just a problem.

00:00:56.208 --> 00:00:57.875
The court wants your head

00:00:58.125 --> 00:00:59.625
to calm Liao's new King.

00:01:00.083 --> 00:01:01.375
I'm only following orders.

00:01:01.791 --> 00:01:02.250
Ninth Prince,

00:01:02.875 --> 00:01:04.458
take your grudge to the ones
who ordered this.

00:01:05.041 --> 00:01:07.208
Don't blame me in the afterlife.

00:01:08.125 --> 00:01:09.291
You speak of loyalty,

00:01:09.875 --> 00:01:10.708
then serve a tyrant.

00:01:11.083 --> 00:01:11.833
Report!

00:01:13.250 --> 00:01:13.791
My lord.

00:01:15.125 --> 00:01:16.958
The Governor's order is to kill him.

00:01:30.333 --> 00:01:32.666
Cao Ming, you dare murder
the Prince of Liao?

00:01:33.166 --> 00:01:35.083
I'm following orders. Take them!

00:01:53.625 --> 00:01:54.958
We all serve the same court.

00:01:54.958 --> 00:01:55.708
Stop killing each other.

00:01:55.708 --> 00:01:57.291
Baihu Shen, you cannot save him.

00:01:58.708 --> 00:01:59.375
Let's go!

00:02:07.208 --> 00:02:08.041
Are you hurt?

00:02:08.875 --> 00:02:09.583
I'm fine.

00:02:14.125 --> 00:02:15.125
What is going on?

00:02:16.250 --> 00:02:17.500
Why would government soldiers
try to kill you?

00:02:18.625 --> 00:02:19.416
And why did we

00:02:20.125 --> 00:02:22.041
end up fighting
the Yunnan Governor's guards?

00:02:38.958 --> 00:02:39.916
Your court

00:02:40.750 --> 00:02:42.625
has recognized Fa Gao's rebel throne.

00:02:43.625 --> 00:02:44.041
Now

00:02:44.291 --> 00:02:46.208
they want to send him my head
as a gift.

00:02:46.916 --> 00:02:47.416
That way,

00:02:47.666 --> 00:02:48.500
Ming can keep

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:49.708
its grip on Liao.

00:02:50.625 --> 00:02:52.750
There is no justice in this world.

00:02:54.791 --> 00:02:55.458
All my life,

00:02:56.250 --> 00:02:57.458
I have been a pawn to throw away.

00:02:58.458 --> 00:02:59.375
I want to live.

00:03:00.291 --> 00:03:01.250
I deserve to live.

00:03:01.875 --> 00:03:02.708
I want to go home.

00:03:03.333 --> 00:03:04.291
That is all I want.

00:03:04.958 --> 00:03:06.791
Why is even that too much to ask?

00:03:09.458 --> 00:03:10.666
Enough.

00:03:10.958 --> 00:03:12.708
We don't have time for despair.

00:03:13.166 --> 00:03:14.166
We need to figure out

00:03:14.583 --> 00:03:15.833
what comes next.

00:03:16.833 --> 00:03:17.833
Our mission

00:03:18.125 --> 00:03:20.000
is to escort Prince Yuanrong
to the border.

00:03:20.833 --> 00:03:21.791
So that is what we do.

00:03:21.791 --> 00:03:22.708
After all this?

00:03:23.583 --> 00:03:25.333
We just fought government soldiers.

00:03:25.333 --> 00:03:26.500
Look at him.

00:03:27.416 --> 00:03:28.958
Do you think he will even make it
to the border alive?

00:03:30.375 --> 00:03:31.625
Even if we get Prince Yuanrong

00:03:31.625 --> 00:03:32.500
to the border,

00:03:32.958 --> 00:03:35.000
how is he supposed to return
and take back his country?

00:03:36.333 --> 00:03:37.083
I can do it.

00:03:37.333 --> 00:03:39.125
Defender-General Ruan Chengtian
guards Liao's border.

00:03:39.416 --> 00:03:40.666
He has always been loyal to my family.

00:03:40.916 --> 00:03:42.458
Get me to the border,

00:03:43.041 --> 00:03:44.375
and I can convince General Ruan

00:03:44.833 --> 00:03:45.791
to raise an army for me
and get back my throne.

00:03:46.541 --> 00:03:48.125
How do you know

00:03:48.125 --> 00:03:49.916
General Ruan is still loyal?

00:03:50.041 --> 00:03:51.833
Bingfan. Hua.

00:03:52.125 --> 00:03:53.833
No one has canceled the mission.

00:03:54.208 --> 00:03:55.750
Let's take Yuanrong to the border.

00:03:56.208 --> 00:03:57.333
If anything goes wrong,

00:03:58.625 --> 00:03:59.458
I will answer for it.

00:03:59.541 --> 00:04:01.166
That is easy to say.

00:04:01.291 --> 00:04:03.000
Enough. Xintian is right.

00:04:03.333 --> 00:04:04.916
Until we receive an order to stop,

00:04:05.083 --> 00:04:06.333
our only mission

00:04:06.541 --> 00:04:07.875
is to get Prince Yuanrong

00:04:07.958 --> 00:04:09.000
safely to the Yunnan border.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.458
There is a border town
called Liangjie.

00:04:10.833 --> 00:04:13.166
People from both sides trade there.

00:04:13.166 --> 00:04:14.458
If we can get him

00:04:14.458 --> 00:04:15.500
to Liangjie safely...

00:04:15.958 --> 00:04:17.791
I can find a way to reach General Ruan.

00:04:19.375 --> 00:04:20.291
There is no time to lose.

00:04:20.333 --> 00:04:20.916
Let's move.

00:04:21.750 --> 00:04:22.333
Go.

00:04:29.166 --> 00:04:31.208
Bingfan, can we stop for a moment?

00:04:31.208 --> 00:04:32.250
Yuanrong feels sick.

00:04:32.583 --> 00:04:33.250
Okay.

00:04:48.458 --> 00:04:49.375
At this pace,

00:04:49.541 --> 00:04:51.833
we should reach Liangjie before sunset.

00:04:52.916 --> 00:04:54.541
No one seems to be following us.

00:04:54.791 --> 00:04:57.333
Of course not.
They can't make this public.

00:04:57.625 --> 00:04:59.250
A public chase would look bad.

00:04:59.958 --> 00:05:02.708
They must have something else planned.

00:05:18.208 --> 00:05:18.833
(Bingfan.)

00:05:18.958 --> 00:05:19.875
(Liao's new King has hired)

00:05:19.875 --> 00:05:20.916
(Tuba Zangxi's assassins)

00:05:20.916 --> 00:05:21.916
(to intercept Fa Yuanrong.)

00:05:21.916 --> 00:05:23.125
(Be extremely careful.)

00:05:23.458 --> 00:05:23.875
Bad news.

00:05:24.250 --> 00:05:25.416
Chang Beiming says

00:05:25.875 --> 00:05:26.791
Liao's new King

00:05:26.875 --> 00:05:28.208
has hired Tuba Zangxi's assassins

00:05:28.958 --> 00:05:30.041
to kill Fa Yuanrong.

00:05:30.208 --> 00:05:30.750
What?

00:05:33.416 --> 00:05:34.208
Tuba Zangxi?

00:05:35.666 --> 00:05:36.166
We are finished.

00:05:37.333 --> 00:05:38.208
They say

00:05:38.666 --> 00:05:39.666
where Tuba Zangxi goes,

00:05:39.916 --> 00:05:40.875
nothing lives.

00:05:41.708 --> 00:05:42.916
If he is really coming,

00:05:43.333 --> 00:05:44.541
none of us can beat him.

00:05:46.083 --> 00:05:46.750
What's your idea?

00:05:56.125 --> 00:05:57.125
Read it yourself.

00:05:59.390 --> 00:06:02.560
(Kill Fa Yuanrong. Redeem yourselves.)

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:04.791
The Commander

00:06:05.833 --> 00:06:08.291
blames us for clashing
with the Yunnan Governor's Office.

00:06:09.291 --> 00:06:10.458
He wants us to make up for it

00:06:11.083 --> 00:06:12.041
by killing Fa Yuanrong.

00:06:12.958 --> 00:06:15.500
No. They told us to protect him.

00:06:15.708 --> 00:06:17.000
Now they want him dead?

00:06:17.416 --> 00:06:18.708
How can they do that?

00:06:20.541 --> 00:06:21.583
How?

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:23.208
Fine.

00:06:23.791 --> 00:06:24.833
Then tell me.

00:06:26.375 --> 00:06:27.916
What choice wouldn't be cruel?

00:06:32.916 --> 00:06:34.125
Bingfan, the court can't

00:06:34.125 --> 00:06:36.458
change its orders overnight
and call that justice.

00:06:37.791 --> 00:06:39.791
Jinyiwei carry out orders.
We don't question them.

00:06:41.375 --> 00:06:42.083
Bingfan.

00:06:48.791 --> 00:06:50.541
They twist the truth
however they please.

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:52.250
They throw lives away for profit.

00:06:52.458 --> 00:06:53.958
How can I obey an order like that?

00:06:54.958 --> 00:06:55.958
Cheng Xintian.

00:06:56.958 --> 00:06:57.916
You are on his side?

00:06:59.083 --> 00:07:00.083
Do you know

00:07:00.083 --> 00:07:01.708
that both Ming and Liao,

00:07:02.541 --> 00:07:04.166
both the court and the martial world,

00:07:04.166 --> 00:07:05.291
want him dead?

00:07:05.583 --> 00:07:06.458
How will you protect him?

00:07:07.791 --> 00:07:08.500
I can't.

00:07:10.208 --> 00:07:11.833
But as long as
there is even the slightest hope,

00:07:12.458 --> 00:07:14.333
I will not let anyone hurt him.

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:22.375
Is there really

00:07:22.375 --> 00:07:23.541
no way to save everyone?

00:07:24.250 --> 00:07:25.708
Young Master Chang's letter
said it clearly.

00:07:26.416 --> 00:07:28.041
Tuba Zangxi's advance team

00:07:28.041 --> 00:07:29.041
has reached Liangjie Town.

00:07:29.375 --> 00:07:30.375
What way is left?

00:07:32.125 --> 00:07:32.750
Hua.

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:35.833
I promised Yuanrong

00:07:37.083 --> 00:07:38.416
I would take him home.

00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:39.750
Xintian.

00:07:40.375 --> 00:07:40.916
Let it go.

00:07:42.458 --> 00:07:43.875
I don't want you

00:07:44.541 --> 00:07:45.333
to turn against each other
because of me.

00:07:45.958 --> 00:07:46.458
Yuanrong.

00:07:48.250 --> 00:07:49.458
I gave you my word.

00:07:50.416 --> 00:07:51.541
I will keep it.

00:07:53.125 --> 00:07:55.500
Cheng Xintian, for him,

00:07:55.958 --> 00:07:57.416
you would risk all our lives?

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:58.583
Hua.

00:08:01.458 --> 00:08:02.250
Have you all lost your minds?

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.375
Can we stop falling apart?

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:07.000
The only way for us to survive now

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:07.875
is to kill him.

00:08:08.208 --> 00:08:08.791
Hua.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.541
Move.

00:08:11.416 --> 00:08:11.875
Hua!

00:08:12.583 --> 00:08:13.625
Hua, put the blade down.

00:08:16.791 --> 00:08:17.958
Please.

00:08:17.958 --> 00:08:19.000
I'm begging you.

00:08:19.416 --> 00:08:20.541
Get that blade away from Hua.

00:08:20.958 --> 00:08:21.666
All of you, stop!

00:08:34.791 --> 00:08:36.500
Bingfan, put it down.

00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:37.333
Haven't you done enough?

00:08:50.166 --> 00:08:51.083
Me?

00:08:54.875 --> 00:08:55.833
For him,

00:08:56.708 --> 00:08:58.083
you would throw away our missions

00:08:58.083 --> 00:09:00.125
and even our friendship?

00:09:04.208 --> 00:09:04.625
Fine.

00:09:06.583 --> 00:09:08.208
Why did I become Jinyiwei?

00:09:09.333 --> 00:09:11.875
So I could survive.

00:09:15.291 --> 00:09:17.125
I don't have extra lives
to die with you.

00:09:18.625 --> 00:09:19.750
You are on your own.

00:09:23.125 --> 00:09:23.833
Hua.

00:09:24.375 --> 00:09:24.916
Hua.

00:09:34.666 --> 00:09:35.250
Bingfan.

00:09:36.875 --> 00:09:39.791
I didn't mean to point my blade
at Hua.

00:09:42.625 --> 00:09:44.625
I really didn't mean to.

00:10:04.500 --> 00:10:06.583
Bingfan. Thank you.

00:10:09.208 --> 00:10:09.916
Xintian.

00:10:10.916 --> 00:10:12.166
Liangjie Town is just ahead.

00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:13.750
Take Fa Yuanrong

00:10:13.958 --> 00:10:14.958
and find another way back to Liao.

00:10:15.875 --> 00:10:16.666
Why?

00:10:17.500 --> 00:10:19.041
Don't you know

00:10:19.250 --> 00:10:20.750
there are bloodthirsty killers

00:10:20.750 --> 00:10:21.625
waiting in that town?

00:10:22.291 --> 00:10:23.416
Do you all want to die there together?

00:10:24.416 --> 00:10:25.166
But Bingfan,

00:10:25.750 --> 00:10:27.291
what about you if we leave?

00:10:28.916 --> 00:10:30.708
I can at least buy you some time.

00:10:31.708 --> 00:10:32.250
No.

00:10:32.500 --> 00:10:33.708
I can't let you stay behind alone.

00:10:33.708 --> 00:10:34.500
I'm going with you.

00:10:37.458 --> 00:10:37.916
We will be too obvious

00:10:37.916 --> 00:10:38.791
if we stay together.

00:10:39.875 --> 00:10:41.041
That is why I have to stay.

00:10:41.208 --> 00:10:42.416
Then I can't leave you alone

00:10:42.416 --> 00:10:43.333
to face Tuba Zangxi.

00:10:43.750 --> 00:10:45.083
I can help too, Bingfan.

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:48.375
What help could either of you be?

00:10:51.625 --> 00:10:53.458
Can either of you stand against
those killers?

00:10:53.875 --> 00:10:55.791
If you stay, you will not help.
You will slow me down.

00:10:58.875 --> 00:11:00.541
Hua, why are you not riding?

00:11:00.541 --> 00:11:01.791
Can't I take a walk?

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:03.041
Why didn't you go with them?

00:11:03.416 --> 00:11:04.625
I want to stay with you.

00:11:04.625 --> 00:11:05.375
Those people...

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.791
All noble words,

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:10.083
but no principles when it counts.

00:11:10.583 --> 00:11:11.583
Shen Bingfan.

00:11:12.166 --> 00:11:14.833
It is bad enough that she always has
to play the hero.

00:11:15.750 --> 00:11:16.625
But when it matters,

00:11:16.625 --> 00:11:18.333
how can she have no sense of teamwork?

00:11:18.541 --> 00:11:19.500
And that sweet little fool.

00:11:20.333 --> 00:11:21.208
She is driving me mad.

00:11:21.500 --> 00:11:22.958
How many times has she even met him?

00:11:23.291 --> 00:11:25.041
Now he is the love of her life?

00:11:26.250 --> 00:11:27.875
If Fa Yuanrong takes back his throne,

00:11:28.166 --> 00:11:29.458
where does she think she fits in?

00:11:29.916 --> 00:11:31.125
Princes have always been fickle.

00:11:31.416 --> 00:11:32.750
How does she not understand
something so simple?

00:11:33.875 --> 00:11:35.625
And for a man,

00:11:35.875 --> 00:11:37.333
she pointed a blade at me.

00:11:38.458 --> 00:11:40.291
And I actually thought of them
as my sisters.

00:11:40.291 --> 00:11:41.625
I must have been blind.

00:11:42.916 --> 00:11:43.583
I'm so mad.

00:11:44.541 --> 00:11:45.500
I joined the Jinyiwei

00:11:45.583 --> 00:11:47.291
so I could live a decent life.

00:11:47.833 --> 00:11:49.791
Risk my life and get dragged down
with them?

00:11:50.166 --> 00:11:51.041
Absolutely not.

00:11:51.208 --> 00:11:52.875
I would have to be out of my mind.

00:11:56.625 --> 00:11:58.208
Why aren't you saying anything?

00:11:59.458 --> 00:12:00.041
Hua.

00:12:00.583 --> 00:12:01.833
You are angry right now.

00:12:01.958 --> 00:12:02.958
I'm afraid I will only upset you more.

00:12:03.541 --> 00:12:05.500
Good. Then don't try to talk me
into anything.

00:12:05.625 --> 00:12:07.000
Even if you do, I'm not going back.

00:12:07.416 --> 00:12:09.375
Don't start with some "sisterhood",

00:12:09.541 --> 00:12:11.500
or guilt me with talk
of leaving them to die.

00:12:11.625 --> 00:12:13.250
I'm not going back to save them.

00:12:13.541 --> 00:12:14.541
And I'm not listening to you.

00:12:15.625 --> 00:12:18.458
Hua. I didn't say anything.

00:12:20.250 --> 00:12:21.375
Yes, sure.

00:12:21.958 --> 00:12:23.208
You didn't say a word.

00:12:23.583 --> 00:12:25.083
Better say nothing.

00:12:25.500 --> 00:12:26.666
Keep your mouth shut for good.

00:12:27.250 --> 00:12:28.625
I won't listen to you anyway.

00:12:29.458 --> 00:12:30.458
Hopeless.

00:12:35.000 --> 00:12:35.625
Bingfan.

00:12:37.833 --> 00:12:39.208
So in your eyes,

00:12:39.708 --> 00:12:41.208
I'm just a burden.

00:12:41.208 --> 00:12:42.250
Aren't you?

00:12:43.458 --> 00:12:44.333
Think about it.

00:12:44.625 --> 00:12:45.958
How much trouble have you caused us?

00:12:46.791 --> 00:12:47.666
Because of you,

00:12:47.833 --> 00:12:49.166
the three of us have turned
against each other.

00:12:49.875 --> 00:12:51.208
And you still say you are not a burden?

00:12:53.125 --> 00:12:54.625
I'm sorry, Bingfan.

00:12:56.750 --> 00:12:58.875
I thought I mattered to you.

00:12:59.875 --> 00:13:02.083
I thought you never saw me as a burden.

00:13:03.250 --> 00:13:04.583
I used to think so too.

00:13:05.125 --> 00:13:06.541
But now I know I was wrong.

00:13:06.625 --> 00:13:07.958
You have always been a burden.

00:13:08.250 --> 00:13:10.458
I should never have backed you
into the Jinyiwei.

00:13:18.666 --> 00:13:20.125
I understand, Bingfan.

00:13:20.666 --> 00:13:21.541
Go!

00:13:40.250 --> 00:13:41.000
Baihu Shen.

00:13:41.958 --> 00:13:43.250
You only want to drive us away.

00:13:43.833 --> 00:13:45.000
Why hurt her like that?

00:13:45.250 --> 00:13:46.708
This all started because of you.

00:13:47.458 --> 00:13:48.416
Get lost!

00:14:11.458 --> 00:14:13.208
Master, the Black and White Reapers

00:14:13.208 --> 00:14:14.041
have entered Liangjie.

00:14:14.125 --> 00:14:14.875
Good.

00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:16.791
Then in Liangjie,

00:14:17.416 --> 00:14:19.166
we end Fa Yuanrong

00:14:19.500 --> 00:14:21.083
and the three female Jinyiwei.

00:14:24.583 --> 00:14:26.791
Hua, are we leaving or not?

00:14:27.375 --> 00:14:29.791
I'm tired. Can't I rest for a moment?

00:14:30.333 --> 00:14:31.750
Fine, fine. Rest.

00:14:33.583 --> 00:14:35.166
You have nothing to say to me?

00:14:39.708 --> 00:14:40.166
Hua.

00:14:40.750 --> 00:14:42.833
If you want to go back,
I will go with you.

00:14:43.250 --> 00:14:44.541
I knew it.

00:14:46.166 --> 00:14:47.625
You were trying to talk me
into going back.

00:14:49.083 --> 00:14:51.125
I'm only going back because of you.

00:14:51.791 --> 00:14:53.541
If it were not for you,

00:14:53.875 --> 00:14:55.916
I wouldn't care whether they lived
or died.

00:14:57.458 --> 00:14:58.125
Hua.

00:14:59.166 --> 00:15:00.625
In my eyes,

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:03.000
you just became even greater.

00:15:04.458 --> 00:15:05.458
What are you talking about?

00:15:06.333 --> 00:15:07.666
Nonsense.

00:15:11.333 --> 00:15:13.791
Hurry up and send Young Master Chang
a pigeon.

00:15:14.041 --> 00:15:15.875
Tell him to come to Liangjie and help.

00:15:18.291 --> 00:15:19.333
I already sent

00:15:19.333 --> 00:15:20.833
the carrier pigeon this afternoon.

00:15:23.083 --> 00:15:25.208
You really do keep things to yourself.

00:15:26.166 --> 00:15:27.833
But you had it all figured out.

00:15:37.458 --> 00:15:39.083
Are we really taking another route
back to Liao?

00:15:41.333 --> 00:15:42.083
Do you really think

00:15:42.958 --> 00:15:44.791
Miss Shen sees you as a burden?

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:52.375
I think
she just doesn't want us to be hurt.

00:15:53.541 --> 00:15:55.833
She wants to hold
off the assassins alone

00:15:56.375 --> 00:15:57.791
and buy us time to escape.

00:15:58.166 --> 00:16:00.166
Doesn't that mean she thinks
I will slow her down?

00:16:00.500 --> 00:16:01.916
That I'm a burden?

00:16:04.916 --> 00:16:06.000
I thought about it too.

00:16:07.416 --> 00:16:08.666
With the time she buys us,

00:16:09.583 --> 00:16:10.541
we could run.

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:11.625
But

00:16:12.583 --> 00:16:14.708
I don't want to be a coward
who flees before battle.

00:16:15.375 --> 00:16:16.166
Xintian.

00:16:17.291 --> 00:16:18.750
Let's go back and help Miss Shen.

00:16:19.208 --> 00:16:20.416
We may not be strong fighters,

00:16:21.291 --> 00:16:22.208
but one more person

00:16:22.750 --> 00:16:23.708
still means one more chance.

00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:25.833
Yuanrong.

00:16:26.416 --> 00:16:27.666
Do you really mean that?

00:16:29.708 --> 00:16:30.916
I'm the Prince of Liao.

00:16:31.291 --> 00:16:32.208
I would rather die fighting

00:16:32.875 --> 00:16:34.000
than survive in shame.

00:16:35.291 --> 00:16:36.333
Yuanrong, you are right.

00:16:36.625 --> 00:16:38.166
We can't leave Bingfan alone.

00:16:38.416 --> 00:16:39.416
We have to help her.

00:16:40.333 --> 00:16:40.750
Go.

00:16:42.470 --> 00:16:46.470
(Liangjie Town)

00:17:34.541 --> 00:17:35.375
Liangjie Town

00:17:35.500 --> 00:17:37.041
has become a city of the living dead.

00:17:37.291 --> 00:17:38.208
And still you dare come?

00:17:38.291 --> 00:17:40.083
I will avenge them.

00:18:08.708 --> 00:18:10.083
- Bingfan!
- Bingfan!

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:14.750
Are you all right?

00:18:38.890 --> 00:18:42.060
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:42.430 --> 00:18:45.810
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:46.060 --> 00:18:49.060
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:49.060 --> 00:18:52.470
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:53.560 --> 00:18:56.770
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:18:57.180 --> 00:19:00.520
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:01.100 --> 00:19:03.310
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:07.350
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:07.350 --> 00:19:11.220
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:14.970
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:15.270 --> 00:19:17.180
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:17.180 --> 00:19:21.720
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:22.020 --> 00:19:23.520
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:23.520 --> 00:19:25.890
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:25.890 --> 00:19:29.770
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:29.770 --> 00:19:32.100
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:32.100 --> 00:19:37.100
♪And run toward this vast life♪